description:
I just received such a great energetic boost and download, I was inspired to extend this class to 7 WEEKS. In this 7 Week Class, we will be covering sooo much more, and I can share with you the Visions and Channeling experiences I had that lead me to teach this to you all. ‚ù§


Our 7 weeks together will be reviewing:

  • Intuitive Eating: Reconnection to the Body
  • Sacred Sexuality: Divine Birth rite of Pleasure
  • Sacred Intonations: Using the power of sound to heal
  • Health is Wealth: Holistic wellness of the Mind Body and Soul
  • Let it Be: the Feminine Art of Being
  • Never not Broken: Sacred Channeled whispers from the Dark Godis
  • Divine Feminine Sister and Brotherhood: Balance and Unity
title: 7 Weeks Revitalizing the Feminine Frequency
